import React from 'react'

import {
    Section,
    Header,
    Title,
    Description,
    RepoContainer,
    Icons,
    StarNumber

} from './styles'

import { BiStar } from "react-icons/bi"

const Repos_Page = (props) => {


    return (
        <Section>
            <Header>{props.number} repositórios</Header>



            <RepoContainer>
                <Title>{props.title}</Title>
                <Description>{props.description}</Description>
                <Icons>
                    <BiStar size={15} /> <StarNumber>{props.star}</StarNumber>
                </Icons>
            </RepoContainer>





        </Section>
    )
}

export default Repos_Page
